<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">海外臨時民主政府 自由香港<br />\nFREE HONG KONG</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/freehongkonghkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreehongkonghkg&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=fc7a3ffd\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/freehongkonghkg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nBMTNBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBMTNBB.jpg&h=16392072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讓這攬炒旗隨風飄揚！（logo已獲攬炒巴授權使用）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人哋北韓都做到 香港唔係做唔到呀嘛？</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共已經決定企硬，連溫和到咁既五大訴求都唔會接受。咁呢個政府仲有咩面代表人民<br />\n<br />\n擇個好日子揀個好地方，設立海外臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n目標係「要使國際社會廣泛相信港共政府為非法政權，爭取外國政府支持，替天行道，天滅中共」<br />\n「因應警察濫用暴力+濫捕事件於國際組織上追究」<br />\n<br />\n最後「推動香港進入real autonomy 嘅時代」<br />\n<br />\n因為而家我哋已經無嘢可以好輸，如果我哋就咁俾場運動完結，最後受害，被批鬥，被清算係每一個真。香港人。前線於是，和理非也如是。警察已經將文革係各中小學重演，唔駛好耐就會到其他界別。"},{"pid":"20eb7563948734a1164a61c479d712bdaec35f50","tid":1567342,"uid":102162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:13:36.000Z","msg":"手足搭輕鐵要小心輕鐵站都有cctv"},{"pid":"6adabd9be583fe3fc72967f3394e3ba61a1adc89","tid":1567342,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5617f2c027d26b03a6704ad5b23b78b966cd35f0","tid":1567342,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">914 天水圍 3pm+愛丁堡2pm<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n915 （國際民主日）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\"